<br>
The servicemen that put themselves in harms way CAN be ready to fight at a moments notice, and they are for the most part good at it But the point is to seem so dangerous to an enemy, to so convince them that to attack would be so costly that they wont attack. They risk themselves and their safety to so protect us in this way and to minimize the possibility of war by being very good at war.<br>
<br>
I have an infinite amount of respect for these people that VOLUNTEER for this because I know first hand what it takes, and what can be asked of you. I know what sacrifices you must willingly make to defend the country you love, and the way of life you hold dear.<br>
